#: index.docbook:266
#, no-c-format
msgid "Moves you one step back in your browsing history of the filesystem."
msgstr ""
"Premakne vas en korak nazaj v zgodovini brskanja po datotečnem sistemu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:270
#, no-c-format
